{"type": "article", "id": 18805, "title": "有机”花盆“", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-10T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607111832q73RZwrHIGQX0gzh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个“花盆”是由三块三角形的薄片像积木一样拼起来的，中间安置了一块圆形的薄片做底，正好可以插进松软的泥土里。它实际上是一个将种子单独分离出来的装置，采用一种特殊的有机材料，可以在自然环境中分解而不破坏环境。不过，放到桌面上做盆景也有一种独特的手工感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111828vWnsbPeMHEjVa4I5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111828i8JwMoYqrP1Uh9QI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111830ePbWs7R1T0DFx4hK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607111830c1APsiVRfBK04bh6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}